headline: PG&E Announces Finalists for 2025 Pitch Fest: 57 Energy- and Climate-Tech Innovators Selected from 400+ Applicants
summary: Pacific Gas and Electric Company (PG&E) today announced the 57 organizations invited to present at its 2025 Pitch Fest, taking place September 23–25 at PG&E's Oakland headquarters.
